Cate Blanchett continued her successful tour of the awards circuit in the US over the weekend despite being drawn into the Woody Allen sex saga.

The 44-year-old actress wore an exquisite dress at the Santa Barbara International Film Festival, where she was awarded with the 2014 Outstanding Performer of the Year Award for her performance in Allen's Blue Jasmine.

